cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.NE 

This paper is about reinforcement learning (RL) and its application to a realistic industrial benchmark. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), which covers RL and related topics. The paper also involves optimization techniques, which could fall under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The use of RL in a real-world setting suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the paper involves neural networks, which could fall under cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
